      <title>美国在“极限施压”的压力下对伊朗实施新制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-unveils-fresh-iran-sanctions-under-maximum-pressure-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部对据称与伊朗向中国运送石油有关的一个金融网络实施制裁，这是特朗普政府首次加大对这个中东国家的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-unveils-fresh-iran-sanctions-under-maximum-pressure-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 16:15:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税生效后，彪马限制中国运动鞋出口至美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/puma-curbs-flow-of-sneakers-from-china-to-us-as-tariffs-kick-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中美贸易战升温，彪马公司 (Puma SE) 向美国出口的中国产运动鞋数量大幅减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/puma-curbs-flow-of-sneakers-from-china-to-us-as-tariffs-kick-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 16:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DOGE 的财政访问权限目前受到法官的部分限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/treasury-access-by-musk-s-doge-partly-limited-by-judge-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国一些工会指责美国财政部非法将其成员信息与埃隆·马斯克的政府效率小组共享之后，一名美国法官暂时限制了工会对美国财政部支付系统的访问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/treasury-access-by-musk-s-doge-partly-limited-by-judge-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 15:46:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟冯德莱恩将向首席执行官推介竞争力计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/eu-s-von-der-leyen-set-to-pitch-ceos-on-competitiveness-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩 (Ursula von der Leyen) 计划于 2 月 26 日会见行业领袖，以向当地顶级生产商保证欧盟将在雄心勃勃的绿色改革期间采取行动提高竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/eu-s-von-der-leyen-set-to-pitch-ceos-on-competitiveness-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 15:32:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果聚焦中国市场 陷入地缘政治斗争中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/apple-s-china-focus-thrusts-it-into-center-of-geopolitical-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司将中国视为其最大的制造中心，将美国视为其最大的市场，但现在它正处于不断升级的地缘政治斗争的漩涡中，有可能涉及关税和监管调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/apple-s-china-focus-thrusts-it-into-center-of-geopolitical-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的贸易选择誓言通过政策恢复“硬实力”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-s-trade-pick-vows-to-restore-hard-power-through-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普提名的美国贸易代表告诉国会议员，他将寻求利用贸易政策振兴制造业和应对“全球动荡”，从而恢复国家的“硬实力”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-s-trade-pick-vows-to-restore-hard-power-through-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:56:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立法者寻求禁止在美国政府设备上使用 DeepSeek 应用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/lawmakers-seek-to-ban-deepseek-app-on-us-government-devices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院情报委员会的两名议员计划于周四提出一项法案，禁止在美国政府发放的设备上使用 DeepSeek 的聊天机器人应用程序，理由是担心其代码与中国共产党有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/lawmakers-seek-to-ban-deepseek-app-on-us-government-devices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 14:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克肆无忌惮的削减成本行动惹恼了共和党参议员和财政部工作人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/elon-musk-s-doge-tactics-annoy-some-republican-allies-of-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当埃隆·马斯克和他的年轻副手团队进入美国政府用来支付账单的财政部计算机网络时，该网络存储了几乎每个美国人的私人财务数据，这在全国引起了恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/elon-musk-s-doge-tactics-annoy-some-republican-allies-of-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赢得债券持有人支持后，厄瓜多尔总统寻求选民支持连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/ecuador-holds-presidential-election-with-noboa-in-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹尼尔·诺沃亚成为厄瓜多尔历史上最年轻的总统时，曾承诺要以紧迫感应对双重犯罪和财政危机。然而，他最大的胜利可能是华尔街。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/ecuador-holds-presidential-election-with-noboa-in-lead</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国援助冻结导致刚果救援工作放缓，尸体横陈街头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-aid-freeze-slows-relief-in-congo-as-bodies-rot-in-streets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府冻结了几乎所有的外国援助，这妨碍了对刚果民主共和国东部人道主义危机的充分响应，上周该地的战斗造成近 3,000 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/us-aid-freeze-slows-relief-in-congo-as-bodies-rot-in-streets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 05:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
